    <item>
      <title>AFK 0.3.0</title>
      <sparkle:version>5</sparkle:version>
      <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.3.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
      <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
      <description><![CDATA[
        <h3>Word-level timestamps + shareable scoreboard</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><b>Timestamps view</b> on file transcripts &mdash; toggle to see every segment with mm:ss times.</li>
          <li><b>Export as .srt or .json</b> from the Save menu (subtitles, video editing, or your own scripts). Also in the CLI: <code>afk transcribe file --srt | --json</code>.</li>
          <li><b>Share card</b> &mdash; one click on Home renders your dictation scoreboard (words, time saved, WPM, rank) as an image, saved to Downloads and copied to the clipboard.</li>
        </ul>
      ]]></description>
