    <item>
      <title>AFK 0.2.1</title>
      <sparkle:version>3</sparkle:version>
      <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.2.1</sparkle:shortVersionString>
      <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
      <description><![CDATA[
        <h3>Recoverable speech-model setup</h3>
        <p>If the first-run speech-model download stalls, you now see what's happening and can fix it:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><b>Live progress + status</b> on Home, Transcribe, and Instructions &mdash; no more silent &ldquo;Preparing the model&hellip;&rdquo;.</li>
          <li><b>Retry button</b> that resumes the download instead of leaving you stuck.</li>
          <li>The download now reliably starts even if onboarding was skipped.</li>
        </ul>
      ]]></description>
